`--subtensor.chain_endpoint wss://test.finney.opentensor.ai:443`

To your bittensor command.  If you've worked your way up to installing a validator, or even installing a miner/server, the testnet won't have the same level of ferocious competition that makes serving on mainnet so incredibly challenging.
